						"title": "Build the future of AI security with Cloudflare",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "Are you a security or IT professional, developer, or enthusiast interested in securing your AI apps and workloads? Join Cloudflare's new user research program for AI security to help us build the next generation of security controls.\n\nWe are looking for individuals to share insights on their AI security challenges and feedback on new features and products. Your perspectives will directly shape Cloudflare services.\n\n__Why join this program?__\n- __Influence the roadmap:__ Shape the features and direction of our product development.\n- __Exclusive access:__ Collaborate with Cloudflare experts to solve your organization's and the industry's challenges\n- __Gain a competitive edge:__ Position yourself as a leader in the rapidly evolving realm of AI security\n\n__What can you expect?__\n- __Interviews & surveys:__ Participate in one-on-one interviews or short surveys to share your experiences.\n- __Early access testing:__ Get hands-on with early-stage prototypes and provide feedback on their usability and effectiveness.\n- __Varied commitment:__ Participation can range from a single 30-minute interview to a series of sessions over a few weeks, depending on your availability and interest.\n\n__Next steps:__ Ready to make a difference in AI security? \n- Express interest now, and we will reach out with more information. \n- Or share simply your feedback on our existing AI security controls via text submission box.\n\n![research program](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/64OvD1Gq81ToWRbEHifeMP/5da7116812d80e5ecc1fb9560afb5440/research_program.png)",
